				\begin{document}$$10 \, \text {kt}$$\end{document} fiducial mass LArTPC modules with integrated photon detection systems (PD systems) [2–4]. In these analyses, we assume all four modules have identical responses. All of the analyses described will use data from the FD, except for the analyses presented in Sects. 7, 8.1, and 10.3, which use data exclusively from the ND.

