In this analysis, we use GLoBES with the MonteCUBES C library, a plugin that replaces the deterministic GLoBES minimizer by a Markov Chain Monte Carlo (MCMC) method that is able to handle higher dimensional parameter spaces. In the simulations we use the configuration for the DUNE TDR [1]. Each point scanned by the MCMC is stored and a frequentist χ2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
