				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$m_{Z'} \lesssim 210~\text {MeV}$$\end{document}. The DUNE sensitivity shown by the solid blue line assumes a measurement of the trident cross section with 40%\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
