				\begin{document}$$\pi ^{+}n \rightarrow K^{+} {\varLambda }$$\end{document}. Figure 28 shows the kinetic energy of a kaon from p→K+ν¯\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
